WEBVTT

00:00.117 --> 00:01.875
Previously on The Royals...

00:01.900 --> 00:03.219
Does this mean anything to you?

00:04.548 --> 00:06.439
She was your father's true love.

00:06.908 --> 00:07.572
She died.

00:07.875 --> 00:10.376
My sister's death
destroyed my family...

00:10.378 --> 00:13.395
and my sister's death
was not an accident.

00:13.397 --> 00:16.347
The day she died, she was
competing in a showjumping event.

00:16.350 --> 00:18.344
When the horse returned,
it was in a sweat.

00:18.369 --> 00:19.251
It was drugged.

00:19.253 --> 00:20.753
She and your mother were rivals.

00:20.755 --> 00:22.288
That's one hell of an accusation!

00:22.290 --> 00:24.323
Our families deserve justice, Ted!

00:24.325 --> 00:26.358
And they deserve to be punished.

00:26.360 --> 00:28.861
You never actually
answered my question.

00:28.863 --> 00:32.430
What happened after so many years
that meant you had to change careers?

00:32.433 --> 00:34.400
I'll tell you what. You guess it

00:34.402 --> 00:35.946
and I'll tell you all about it.

00:37.772 --> 00:40.806
If this was all just about
taking things from me...

00:41.943 --> 00:43.576
Here, take these.

00:45.846 --> 00:47.296
Violet, I love you.

00:47.298 --> 00:49.615
Did you just say, "love"?

00:49.617 --> 00:51.150
Yes. I love you.

00:51.152 --> 00:52.918
You know what's not helping?

00:52.920 --> 00:54.703
The fact that you never said it back.

00:54.705 --> 00:56.222
You need to breathe.

00:56.224 --> 00:58.908
My grandmother gave me something
that made it all better.

00:58.910 --> 01:01.994
I'm going to get it for you.
I want you to have it.

01:02.296 --> 01:04.930
I'll be back before the broadcast.
I promise.

01:04.932 --> 01:08.284
Cyrus has picked out
an engagement ring.

01:08.286 --> 01:10.269
Thanks to your Bill of Succession,

01:10.271 --> 01:12.571
if they're still married when he dies,

01:12.573 --> 01:15.874
she will be the sole reigning monarch.

01:16.611 --> 01:19.578
I'm not close to you, Helena,
because you're my daughter.

01:19.580 --> 01:21.780
I'm close to you because
you're the Queen.

01:25.562 --> 01:27.032
I think Mum killed someone.

01:29.000 --> 01:35.074
