01:36.847 --> 01:38.283
I'm not sure I know how to answer that.

01:40.034 --> 01:41.251
We're just a family, you know?

01:42.503 --> 01:43.525
Like any family.

01:45.606 --> 01:46.657
And then we're not.

01:48.042 --> 01:49.892
(CYRUS) You're lying! (HELENA) I'm not!

01:49.894 --> 01:53.746
(CYRUS) Tell the truth or you won't live
to see another lying, cheating day!

01:53.748 --> 01:55.364
(HELENA) Get off me!

01:55.366 --> 01:58.417
(CYRUS) You think I'm stupid?
You think I'm paranoid?

01:58.419 --> 02:00.085
I think you're coked out of your mind

02:00.087 --> 02:01.553
and don't know what you're doing!

02:01.555 --> 02:04.356
You've been threatened ever
since I fell in love with her.

02:04.358 --> 02:06.925
Cyrus, remove the Great Sword
of State from my throat

02:06.927 --> 02:09.695
or you are going to lose your
last remaining testicle.

02:09.697 --> 02:10.829
Ow!

02:10.830 --> 02:12.865
You kicked my balls!

02:12.867 --> 02:15.701
- I kicked your ball.
- You bitch!

02:15.703 --> 02:17.519
You tell me what you did with her!

02:17.521 --> 02:18.587
Tell me!

02:18.643 --> 02:19.758
Agh!

02:20.775 --> 02:21.415
(Sighs)

02:22.009 --> 02:24.306
People are sleeping, for Godsakes!

02:26.380 --> 02:29.181
Cyrus, get up, you're not that hurt.

02:29.183 --> 02:31.884
- Stop being so dramatic.
(ELEANOR) Mum?

02:32.720 --> 02:33.774
(Glass smashes)

02:33.799 --> 02:35.214
- sync and corrections by Caio -
- www.addic7ed.com -

02:35.239 --> 02:36.297
(Cell phone buzzes)

02:46.077 --> 02:46.751
Yeah.

02:47.168 --> 02:48.235
Your Majesty?

02:51.122 --> 02:52.738
You believe this shit?

02:52.740 --> 02:55.074
- Slow down.
- She attacked me.

02:55.076 --> 02:57.042
Hit me over the head
with a goddamn vase.

02:57.044 --> 02:58.410
She could have killed me.

02:58.412 --> 03:01.246
The Grand Duchess claims she was
defending Her Majesty the Queen.

03:01.248 --> 03:03.349
They did something, Pryce. To Violet.

03:03.351 --> 03:04.983
They're in cahoots, those two.

03:04.985 --> 03:06.885
Your Majesty, please, take a seat.

03:06.887 --> 03:08.064
(Sighs)

03:10.057 --> 03:13.275
You say Violet's gone missing. Okay.

03:13.277 --> 03:15.060
When was the last time
you heard from her?

03:15.062 --> 03:16.495
Last night.

03:16.497 --> 03:18.697
She said she wanted to
get something for me,

03:18.699 --> 03:19.868
she said she loved me...

03:19.893 --> 03:22.101
or at least she implied that she did,

03:22.103 --> 03:24.036
and then she said she'd
be straight back.

03:24.038 --> 03:25.504
And this was before your speech?

03:25.506 --> 03:27.139
Yes, but she never came back.

03:27.141 --> 03:30.509
So you ingested copious
quantities of various drugs,

03:30.511 --> 03:33.362
chased them with a 60-year-old
single malt Scotch

03:33.364 --> 03:36.065
and attacked the Queen of England
with the Great Sword of State.

03:36.067 --> 03:38.117
At which point, the
Grand Duchess of Oxford

03:38.119 --> 03:40.452
broke a 15th-century Imperial
vase over your head,

03:40.454 --> 03:41.820
rendering you unconscious.

03:42.423 --> 03:45.023
Would you say that was an
accurate account of things?

03:45.751 --> 03:47.499
It sounds worse when you say it.

03:49.130 --> 03:51.563
Due to Your Majesty's
recent public appearances,

03:51.565 --> 03:54.099
there have been a higher than
usual number of threats.

03:54.101 --> 03:57.102
I would like to restrict access
today, monitor things closely.

03:57.104 --> 03:59.938
All delivery personnel. Flowers. Food.

03:59.940 --> 04:01.790
- Anyone in and out.
- Boring.

04:02.321 --> 04:03.342
But...

04:03.806 --> 04:05.043
do you think these threats

04:05.045 --> 04:08.030
have anything to do with
Violet's disappearance?

04:08.759 --> 04:10.916
I couldn't live with myself
if that were the case.

04:10.918 --> 04:12.684
Let's not get ahead of ourselves.

04:14.025 --> 04:16.755
Your Majesty, why do you
think the Queen is involved?

04:17.591 --> 04:19.048
Well, she knew about the ring.

04:19.959 --> 04:21.627
I selected an engagement ring

04:21.629 --> 04:23.962
from the royal collection
and she knew about it.

04:24.298 --> 04:26.715
If I were to marry, she
would no longer be Queen

04:26.717 --> 04:28.283
nor next in line to the throne.

04:29.048 --> 04:32.671
She'd stop at nothing
to protect her station.

04:32.673 --> 04:34.640
Even murder?

04:34.642 --> 04:36.942
People kill people all
the time around here.

04:36.944 --> 04:38.744
Where've you been, Pryce?

04:39.814 --> 04:42.948
Sorry, that was insensitive
considering all you've been through.

04:42.950 --> 04:44.517
You've had a rough morning.

04:46.887 --> 04:48.437
Let's retrace your steps.

04:48.439 --> 04:50.856
Following your broadcast
yesterday, what did you do?

04:51.659 --> 04:55.837
I was worried about Violet so I came
back to my room and put some music on.

04:56.197 --> 04:56.993
What then?

04:59.400 --> 05:01.066
(BILL WITHERS: Ain't No Sunshine)

05:01.068 --> 05:02.901
♪ Ain't no sunshine when she's gone ♪

05:05.289 --> 05:09.558
♪ It's not warm when she's away ♪

05:09.560 --> 05:11.310
(Snorts)

05:11.812 --> 05:15.247
♪ Ain't no sunshine when she's gone ♪

05:15.249 --> 05:18.100
♪ And she's always gone too long ♪

05:18.102 --> 05:22.221
♪ Any time she goes away ♪

05:23.874 --> 05:25.641
♪ Wonder this time... ♪

05:25.643 --> 05:26.829
Cyrus?

05:30.731 --> 05:33.866
Thank God you're back!

05:35.436 --> 05:37.853
Oh, I love you so much.

05:37.855 --> 05:40.873
(HELENA) Cyrus? Cyrus?

05:42.470 --> 05:43.275
I thought...

05:44.512 --> 05:46.345
How many drugs did you do tonight?

05:46.347 --> 05:47.306
Um... a few.

05:47.892 --> 05:48.985
You need to sit down.

05:49.356 --> 05:50.491
I can't.

05:51.534 --> 05:53.655
I can't eat. I can't sleep.

05:54.305 --> 05:55.554
Where could she be?

05:55.556 --> 05:57.523
Calm down and talk to me.

05:57.525 --> 05:59.157
Did anything happen before she left?

05:59.159 --> 06:00.592
- Did you argue?
- No.

06:00.594 --> 06:02.060
I told her I loved her.

06:02.062 --> 06:04.062
I see...

06:04.064 --> 06:06.615
I didn't scare her off, if
that's what you're thinking.

06:06.617 --> 06:09.568
- Did she say it back?
- I didn't scare her off.

06:09.889 --> 06:11.092
I'm sure she's fine.

06:11.372 --> 06:13.839
But... perhaps considering
the pace of things,

06:13.841 --> 06:15.507
she simply needs a bit of space.

06:15.509 --> 06:17.659
Do you think that's it?

06:17.995 --> 06:21.213
You haven't known her long and already
you've picked out an engagement ring

06:21.215 --> 06:22.342
and told her you love her.

06:23.942 --> 06:25.217
How do you know about that?

06:25.719 --> 06:28.070
You just told me, Breaking Bad.

06:32.803 --> 06:34.552
About the engagement ring.

06:36.497 --> 06:38.630
The Crown Jeweler's got
a wandering tongue.

06:38.632 --> 06:40.282
You know what this place is like.

06:40.284 --> 06:43.969
The point is, you might have
overwhelmed the poor girl

06:43.971 --> 06:46.071
or her cell phone could have run low.

06:46.073 --> 06:48.407
- How long's she been gone?
- Five hours.

06:48.409 --> 06:51.443
Oh, for Godsakes,
Cyrus, she'll be fine.

06:51.445 --> 06:53.478
And, if she doesn't show up,

06:53.480 --> 06:57.282
you have to accept the fact that
you're the King of England.

06:58.168 --> 07:00.385
Being Queen is not for everyone.

07:02.656 --> 07:03.686
Get some rest.

07:05.326 --> 07:08.694
♪ Any time she goes away ♪

07:15.669 --> 07:17.436
(Sighs)

07:19.540 --> 07:21.540
Answer...

07:36.991 --> 07:39.925
♪ I keep my ears to the ground ♪

07:39.927 --> 07:41.710
♪ My eyes wide shut ♪

07:41.712 --> 07:43.679
♪ I'm boiling over, baby ♪

07:43.681 --> 07:45.647
♪ Yeah, hot to the touch ♪

07:45.649 --> 07:48.767
♪ I dance to the drum of my own heart ♪

07:48.769 --> 07:51.069
♪ Tells me when to move ♪

07:51.071 --> 07:53.255
♪ Says it's time to start ♪

07:53.257 --> 07:55.140
(Sniffs)

08:04.051 --> 08:05.384
(Snorts violently)

08:12.426 --> 08:14.426
'She said she'd be straight back.'

08:14.428 --> 08:15.827
I'll be back before the broadcast.

08:15.829 --> 08:18.430
- Violet
- I'll be back before the broadcast.

08:18.942 --> 08:20.809
She's the frigging maid.

08:21.602 --> 08:24.936
(KING SIMON) 'Maybe your sins can
be covered up in this lifetime.'

08:25.572 --> 08:28.340
But eventually, we all
pay for our sins.

08:28.342 --> 08:30.359
- 'Violet.'
- 'I love you.'

08:30.361 --> 08:32.510
- 'She said she loved me.'
- Of course I do.

08:32.513 --> 08:35.414
(Echoing) 'Of course I do.'

08:35.416 --> 08:37.649
You'll remain the Queen of
England until I marry again.

08:37.650 --> 08:39.618
She's the frigging maid.

08:41.438 --> 08:43.422
'The Great Sword of State.'

08:59.073 --> 09:03.075
..from my throat or you are going to
lose your last remaining testicle!

09:03.077 --> 09:04.409
Ow!

09:04.411 --> 09:06.161
You kicked my balls!

09:06.163 --> 09:09.081
- I kicked your ball.
- You bitch!

09:09.083 --> 09:11.883
Tell me what you did with her! Tell me!

09:11.885 --> 09:13.418
Agh!

09:14.088 --> 09:15.554
(Sighs)

09:15.556 --> 09:17.906
People are sleeping, for Godsakes!

09:32.300 --> 09:33.355
Yeah.

09:33.968 --> 09:36.786
(MY DOUBLE, MY BROTHER: Bound To Break)

09:36.788 --> 09:39.372
♪ And I fought my demons again ♪

09:39.880 --> 09:43.582
♪ A rock in the ocean, the waters spin ♪

09:43.967 --> 09:48.520
♪ And the waves crash down,
but the stone's not moving ♪

09:50.291 --> 09:52.257
Do you think they killed her?

09:52.259 --> 09:55.227
Oh, please, not now.

09:55.229 --> 09:58.163
Can't we just go back to the
dream I was having about you

09:58.165 --> 10:01.400
without all the killing and the
blood and the constant guilt?

10:03.003 --> 10:05.370
No. You can't.

10:05.372 --> 10:07.272
It's too late for that now.

10:09.410 --> 10:12.928
Jasper Frost has been
investigating the King's attack.

10:12.930 --> 10:14.947
Pulling surveillance tapes.

10:14.949 --> 10:16.882
Harassing Scotland Yard.

10:16.884 --> 10:18.450
Why? The King's killer has confessed.

10:18.452 --> 10:20.485
Maybe he thinks it wasn't Lucius.

10:20.487 --> 10:22.221
Maybe he knows it was you.

10:24.124 --> 10:26.275
He's handsome.

10:26.277 --> 10:28.160
(Laughs)

10:30.014 --> 10:31.613
Jasper.

10:31.615 --> 10:33.799
(Giggles)

10:33.801 --> 10:35.567
Younger than you.

10:35.569 --> 10:37.669
Smarter.

10:37.671 --> 10:39.638
- Mmm...
- Please stop.

10:39.640 --> 10:41.306
(Cell phone buzzes)

10:45.529 --> 10:47.179
Yes, Your Majesty.

10:47.181 --> 10:49.314
I'll be right there.

10:51.452 --> 10:53.201
Off you go.

10:53.921 --> 10:56.088
King's bitch.

11:01.862 --> 11:03.929
(Moans softly)

11:06.433 --> 11:08.133
Hello, Foxy.

11:08.135 --> 11:11.837
You're standing on my ceiling.

11:11.839 --> 11:13.705
If you right yourself, I
promise to come down.

11:13.707 --> 11:15.641
(Groans)

11:22.182 --> 11:24.716
I thought we had an
understanding, Foxy.

11:24.718 --> 11:26.218
About my lifestyle.

11:26.220 --> 11:27.986
It's all still here.

11:28.989 --> 11:31.340
Cocaine, marijuana, MDMA

11:31.342 --> 11:33.659
and assorted hallucinogens... here.

11:35.129 --> 11:36.995
Okay, then.

11:36.997 --> 11:38.764
- Well done, you.
- Thank you.

11:40.901 --> 11:42.367
What's that?

11:42.369 --> 11:44.903
It's a gift. From Mr. Frost.

11:44.905 --> 11:46.538
I'll leave you to it.

11:46.540 --> 11:48.307
Wait.

11:48.309 --> 11:50.208
Stay put.

12:00.621 --> 12:03.021
We have constant surveillance on Ms.
Cook,

12:03.023 --> 12:05.958
and can apprehend her immediately
if that's what you'd wish.

12:05.960 --> 12:08.727
Of course, Mr. Frost would
be implicated as well.

12:09.530 --> 12:12.831
Also, I'd like to apologize personally.

12:15.402 --> 12:16.535
Why you?

12:16.537 --> 12:18.804
For suggesting you phone a friend.

12:19.356 --> 12:22.107
I should have known that all
your friends would be shit.

12:25.813 --> 12:28.580
There's a slight chance you
might amuse me, Mr. Hill.

12:30.651 --> 12:34.102
You were on the trail
of a master criminal...

12:34.104 --> 12:35.554
No.

12:35.556 --> 12:37.873
I'll guess it eventually.

12:40.461 --> 12:42.310
Wow.

12:42.312 --> 12:44.196
It's about time.

12:44.198 --> 12:47.099
- What's about time?
- The drug thing is getting a little old.

12:47.101 --> 12:49.167
Oh! So's the sleeping
with models thing.

12:50.004 --> 12:53.038
Wasn't a great example.
What do you want?

12:53.040 --> 12:55.574
I wanna find out if Mum's an
assassin and I wanna do it now.

12:55.576 --> 12:57.743
I've been up all night and
I'm in a horrible mood.

12:57.745 --> 13:00.262
Well, I've been up all night too, Liam,

13:00.264 --> 13:02.247
and I'm horny, so deal with it.

13:03.584 --> 13:05.417
Fine. Give me the photo.

13:05.419 --> 13:06.651
Stay here.

13:06.653 --> 13:08.270
Why?

13:08.272 --> 13:10.122
Because, believe it or not,

13:10.124 --> 13:12.624
Mum and I had a really
great day yesterday,

13:12.626 --> 13:14.926
and I want to give her
the benefit of the doubt

13:14.928 --> 13:17.079
before we start calling her a murderer.

13:17.081 --> 13:18.530
I'll be back.

13:24.538 --> 13:27.823
Cyrus, get off, you're not that hurt.

13:27.825 --> 13:30.809
- Stop being so dramatic.
(ELEANOR) Mum?

13:32.246 --> 13:34.329
(Door opens)

13:34.948 --> 13:36.882
Ah! Eleanor.

13:36.884 --> 13:39.151
- What, darling?
- What's going on?

13:39.153 --> 13:40.619
What do you mean?

13:40.621 --> 13:42.220
You seem shifty.

13:42.222 --> 13:44.489
Yeah, well, you seem bulimic.

13:44.491 --> 13:46.425
What do you want?

13:46.427 --> 13:48.060
Uh... I...

13:48.062 --> 13:50.912
I found this photo of you and
I want to show it to you.

13:50.914 --> 13:52.581
Look how pretty you look.

13:53.333 --> 13:55.600
Ah... Well, long time ago.

13:56.170 --> 13:57.702
Mm-hm.

13:57.704 --> 14:00.555
Who's that? That girl.

14:01.391 --> 14:03.375
Hmm...

14:03.377 --> 14:04.743
I don't recall.

14:04.745 --> 14:06.545
Just some girl.

14:09.450 --> 14:11.116
Yeah, okay.

14:11.118 --> 14:14.352
But if you leave it with me, I could
try to find out more if you like.

14:17.040 --> 14:18.507
No, that's okay.

14:20.594 --> 14:23.361
Eleanor, we had a nice day
yesterday, didn't we?

14:24.731 --> 14:26.765
Did we?

14:39.012 --> 14:41.079
- Well?
- You were right.

14:41.081 --> 14:43.014
The bitch did it.

14:45.511 --> 14:46.556
What do we do now?

14:55.608 --> 14:58.046
She'd do anything to protect
her station.

14:58.612 --> 14:59.693
Even murder?

14:59.718 --> 15:02.264
People kill people all
the time around here.

15:02.466 --> 15:04.666
Where have you been, Pryce?

15:05.070 --> 15:06.450
Sorry, that was insensitive.

15:07.271 --> 15:08.804
Are you sure?

15:08.806 --> 15:10.423
They said the word "murder".

15:10.425 --> 15:12.274
So do you think Ted knows about it?

15:12.276 --> 15:15.678
I asked him to look into the
Domino symbol on my medallion.

15:16.614 --> 15:18.147
Maybe he knows more than we do.

15:18.149 --> 15:20.416
And, of course, Cyrus knows about it.

15:21.185 --> 15:22.785
Ahhh, I knew it!

15:23.588 --> 15:25.588
She lied to me about that photo.

15:25.590 --> 15:27.556
Straight to my face.

15:27.558 --> 15:29.809
And then she had the
balls to say to me,

15:29.811 --> 15:32.862
"We had a nice day yesterday,
didn't we, Eleanor?"

15:32.864 --> 15:36.832
"Yeah, Mum, a great day, right up until
I found out you killed someone!"

15:38.086 --> 15:39.935
I'm sorry, Len.

15:41.722 --> 15:44.573
I guess I'll head back to my
creepy clean room and get high.

15:45.159 --> 15:48.644
Let me know when you want to confront
our murderous mother, won't you?

15:55.570 --> 15:57.787
It just keeps getting
worse, doesn't it?

15:59.857 --> 16:01.390
