16:09.233 --> 16:11.567
Pretty flowers.

16:11.569 --> 16:14.770
Like the ones on my grave thanks
to you getting me killed.

16:15.173 --> 16:18.774
But then, people kill people
all the time around here.

16:19.177 --> 16:20.409
Don't they, baby?

